        <briefdescription>
<para>Retrieves the conn_mgr binding struct for a provided iface if it exists. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Bindings for connectivity implementations with missing API structs are ignored.</para>
<para>For use only by connectivity implementations.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>iface</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>- bound network interface to obtain the binding struct for. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>struct conn_mgr_conn_binding* Pointer to the retrieved binding struct if it exists, NULL otherwise. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
