          <type>struct <ref refid="structconn__mgr__conn__binding" kindref="compound">conn_mgr_conn_binding</ref> *</type>
          <declname>binding</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Lock the passed-in binding, making it safe to access. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Call this whenever accessing binding data, unless inside a <ref refid="structconn__mgr__conn__api" kindref="compound">conn_mgr_conn_api</ref> callback, where it is called automatically by conn_mgr.</para>
<para>Reentrant.</para>
<para>For use only by connectivity implementations.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>binding</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>- Binding to lock </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
